description.en:
The Nifty ONEz is a shard that consists of NFT artworks of  JOSIE, PRANKSIE, GOLDWEARD, POLETTI, PR1MAL CYPHER, OSINACHI, and many more.

The Portfolio includes CryptoArt from 20 of the hottest artists in the emerging NFT art scene. Some of the art is from OCs (Original Cryptoartists) whose early work helped launch the space while other artwork is from artists that are quickly making a name for themselves.
